OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold on
OL,6,FFriday and Saturday with scattered
OL,7,Fwintry showers, these mainly across
OL,8,Fthe west. Rain spreading east followed
OL,9,Fby showers on Sunday.
